Title: Tomorrow War
Descript: A family man is drafted to fight in a future war where the fate of humanity relies on his ability to confront the past.

Title: Boss Level
Descript: A retired Special Forces officer is trapped in a never-ending time loop on the day of his death.

Title: Reminiscence
Descript: Nick Bannister, a private investigator of the mind, navigates the alluring world of the past when his life is changed by new client Mae. A simple case becomes an obsession after she disappears and he fights to learn the truth about her.
